description: Retrieves a list of all security configurations.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the security configuration.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimeStamp
nested_items.description: The time at which this security configuration was created.

nested_items.name: EncryptionConfiguration
nested_items.description: The encryption configuration associated with this security configuration.

nested_items.name: S3Encryption
nested_items.description: The encryption configuration for Amazon Simple Storage Service (Amazon S3) data.

nested_items.name: S3EncryptionMode
nested_items.description: The encryption mode to use for Amazon S3 data.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the KMS key to be used to encrypt the data.

nested_items.name: CloudWatchEncryption
nested_items.description: The encryption configuration for Amazon CloudWatch.

nested_items.name: CloudWatchEncryptionMode
nested_items.description: The encryption mode to use for CloudWatch data.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the KMS key to be used to encrypt the data.

nested_items.name: JobBookmarksEncryption
nested_items.description: The encryption configuration for job bookmarks.

nested_items.name: JobBookmarksEncryptionMode
nested_items.description: The encryption mode to use for job bookmarks data.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the KMS key to be used to encrypt the data.

nested_items.name: DataQualityEncryption
nested_items.description: The encryption configuration for Glue Data Quality assets.

nested_items.name: DataQualityEncryptionMode
nested_items.description: The encryption mode to use for encrypting Data Quality assets. These assets include data quality rulesets, results, statistics, anomaly detection models and observations.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the KMS key to be used to encrypt the data.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A continuation token, if there are more security configurations to return.
